<li id="cite_note-Scott-9">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Scott_9-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Scott_9-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Scott_9-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Scott_9-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFScott_M._Martin">Scott M. Martin (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2002-09-24"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-24"><a href="/wiki/September_24" title="September 24">September 24</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2002" title="2002">2002</a></span>). "<a href="http://llr.lls.edu/volumes/v36-issue1/martin-original1.pdf" class="external text" title="http://llr.lls.edu/volumes/v36-issue1/martin-original1.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Mythology of the Public Domain: Exploring the Myths Behind Attacks on the Duration of Copyright Protection</a>" (PDF). <i>Loyola of Los Angeles Law Review</i> (Loyola Law Review) <b>36</b> (1): 280. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/issn/1533-5860" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/issn/1533-5860" rel="nofollow">1533-5860</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://llr.lls.edu/volumes/v36-issue1/martin-original1.pdf" class="external free" title="http://llr.lls.edu/volumes/v36-issue1/martin-original1.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://llr.lls.edu/volumes/v36-issue1/martin-original1.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-11-17</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+Mythology+of+the+Public+Domain%3A+Exploring+the+Myths+Behind+Attacks+on+the+Duration+of+Copyright+Protection&amp;rft.jtitle=Loyola+of+Los+Angeles+Law+Review&amp;rft.aulast=Scott+M.+Martin&amp;rft.au=Scott+M.+Martin&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BSeptember+24%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B2002%5D%5D&